item.title: Our First Kiss
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: It wasn't that long, and it certainly wasn't the kind of kiss you see in movies these days, but it was wonderful in its own way, and all I can remember about the moment is that when our lips touched, I knew the memory would last forever.

item.title: Got Engaged
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Her boyfriend gives her a Mercedes, [her friends] say, 'Oh, that's nice.' But her boyfriend gives her a diamond, they say, 'Oh, he's serious.' It's not just the gift of love-it's the gift of commitment. She's not jumping up and down because she got a diamond ring but because she got a guy!

item.title: Got Married
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Marriage has made me a lot happier and I'm deeply in love with my wife, and I thank God for her every day.

item.title: I'm Pregnant
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Of course I can do this. I'm pregnant, not brain-damaged. My condition doesn't change my personality.

item.title: Welcome Michael!
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Welcome Our new little family member, he is so cute and we still afraid to hurt him as we really don't have experience with newborn, excuse us Michael!
